text: Their prices are cheaper then most local hawker stalls that sell japanese food. For the price, have to lower your expectation on the presentation of the food. Can call it econ japanese rice but for the price is reasonable
I didn't even get to order, auntie serving us ignored me and took the next person in line. I walked away after that happened because I had already waited for a few minutes.

Best Bibimbap in Hougang! And also Northeastern Singapore! Serving is generous and taste is just NICE! Affordable price! Great variety, totally spoiled for choice! Waiting time is short! The stall will closed about 8pm. Boss and staff are friendly, responsive and welcoming. Will visit them soon! CHEERS!!!ğŸ‘ğŸ‘ğŸ‘ğŸ‘ğŸ‘
